## ITelemetryOperationResult.startTimestampMs property

> This API is provided as a preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

A timestamp in milliseconds (from `performance.now()`<></>) when the operation started. If the operation was blocked, will be `undefined`<></>.

**Signature:**

```typescript
startTimestampMs?: number;
```
